See https://honk.sigxcpu.org/piki/projects/git-buildpackage/

Upstream signature support
==========================

import-dsc:
  - import signature if part of dsc file

import-orig:
  - symlink when symlinking upstream tarball if present
  - commit to pristine-tar branch

export-orig:
  - symlink signature if present
  - export from pristine-tar branch if present

pristine-tar:
  - commit signature file if present


Signature modes (--upstream-signatures)
=======================================
  - yes: force checkin/checkout of sigs
  - no: always ignore signatures
  - auto: checkin/checkout signatures if present

